{"tid":1175073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歹徒爆竊運動用品店 波鞋多到擸唔晒","createTime":"2019-05-28T10:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T13:50:38.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"457deffe3217632fbb8b89f90fbf33fa182761ec","tid":1175073,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJznCdG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJznCdG.png&h=bd290cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yj93mFn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyj93mFn.png&h=2c4e2af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角花園街75號一間運動用品店遭賊人爆竊。中午12時19分，職員報警指，失去一批營業額及貨品，包括波鞋和cap帽，總值約5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，初步相信賊人由後巷爬入天井，再潛入店舖搜掠，天井鐵閘還夾住兩盒波鞋，估計是賊人匆忙間遺下。"},{"pid":"d242f7c2deb67b782d372cfda7d8f97cd6ec623f","tid":1175073,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"5萬蚊貨都偷洗唔洗窮成咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}